{"tid":1264275,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[反送中都不一定不會投建制]急需鍵盤戰士！請入FB各區各屋邨群組，慎防建制派小鮮肉入侵人心","createTime":"2019-06-28T15:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T04:46:02.000Z","uid":270000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"49fb199f1909406ea132a35c19653c29c5c5ddf4","tid":1264275,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到有街坊喺fb屋邨group post鄘仔登上外國報紙的新聞，下面竟然見到有街坊話：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">X仔！你都得架，加油！</span></span><br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而X仔係建制派旗下的年輕社區幹事</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n再追Post，又見到有人講緊<span style=\"color: purple;\">反送中</span>，下面有街坊留言問佢支唔支持<span style=\"color: violet;\">國歌法、明日大嶼、真普選</span>等，而佢話咩<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">一半一半</span>，又話要<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">再做多D功課先答到</span>，但個街坊竟然話：<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我估佢係忠嘅！</span></strong><br />\n&hellip;&hellip;然後有街坊和應。仲要加句：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力，不割蓆不內亂呀！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你會好清楚見到，建制派在地區以蛇齋餅粽拉攏的人心，你以為這麼容易被推翻嗎？反送中既人一樣有機會投建制。<br />\n因為D建制派小鮮肉，成日講：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我一心為地區服務，我唔搞政治！</span></span></strong><br />\n加上佢地平日狂落區，見到街坊就笑口（西西？），平日咁忙的香港人，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">都係睇印象投票架咋</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n面對呢Ｄ「只想服務地區論」，我地可以做嘅係，入你果區/屋邨/鄰近屋邨的地區fb group，每見到有人支持X仔，就去同佢傾下，點出地區一樣會關政治事，例如係，比X仔入左區議會，佢投票時，點確保佢唔會跟從黨的意志？<br />\n仲有其他駁斥的方法嗎？好嬲的我暫時諗唔到了&hellip;&hellip;各位鍵盤戰士可以一起出一分力嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n制敵秘訣：記得鋪陳該小鮮肉所屬政黨／政治組織<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">罪證</span>，並保持<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">理性語調</span>，呢D小鮮肉有個共通點係，一遇到有人點出佢地既問題時，就會起晒鋼，又串咀又剩，你再惹多佢兩下，佢隨時冇晒形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但亦因為街坊好着重「印象」，如果你太串咀／比街坊感覺欺人太甚，令街坊覺得呢位X仔好可憐，咁就molamola<br />\n所以謹記，要以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">理性中帶點暗串但又保持禮貌</span></span>地去進攻。<br />\n<br />\n加油呀兄弟!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3d71af8ecfab4b6acba5a8918a60ed329e2e69","tid":1264275,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10514aeb79df34f128652ea5f6a63cd9c54194e4","tid":1264275,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T16:09:26.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9118a514b6f05c7a621162fe58fdd83e442322b1","tid":1264275,"uid":65045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T17:15:50.000Z","msg":"泛民一直就係太focus喺政治而忽略地區民生工作，ignore咗一班唔care政治嘅人，你要spin去政治好易有反效果。經過今次反送中都未醒嘅人好難再用政治說服佢哋。況且當區建制人已經得到佢哋信任，你好難同佢哋講一路幫緊佢哋嘅人其實都係衰人。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋care嘅係眼前貼身嘅野，雖然我哋資源冇得同建制鬥，但係我哋有一班熱血人。如果每區都成立一條地區服務team，踏實關心嗰區嘅民生議題，同街坊混熟，畀啲甜頭佢哋，慢慢拉攏人心先push民主意識會比較適合。"},{"pid":"a464062b82f76fefeb7888977fe168bdc7a4d773","tid":1264275,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:16:02.000Z","msg":"其實街坊未必冇民主意識呢，有人係支持真普選，亦會問果位建制派o靚仔支唔支持，個o靚仔含糊其辭就過左骨，所以更需要有人提醒D街坊，建制派o靚仔都係跟黨投票架咋<br />\n<br />\n而且今次反送中後，應該多左人會理政治，你同佢講返果d o靚仔所屬政黨的投票紀錄，係有得挽回的"},{"pid":"12f3fa2a7a3f38b7e7adebf99ecad3609df312f0","tid":1264275,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}